                      </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul
                      class="
                        mega-menu-column
                        sub-menu-container
                        col-lg-4
                        border-left-0
                      "
                    >
                      <li class="mega-menu-title menu-item">
                        <a class="menu-link" href="#"><div>FAQs</div></a>
                        <ul class="sub-menu-container">
                          <li class="menu-item">
                            <a class="menu-link" href="#"
                              ><div>Q. How do I purchase an item?</div></a
                            >
